  <releases>
    <release version="48.0" date="2025-03-14">
      <description>
        <ul>
          <li>Add support for battery charge limiting</li>
          <li>Add Wellbeing settings</li>
          <li>Add monitor HDR settings in the Display settings</li>
          <li>Add separated "Power Saving" settings page</li>
          <li>Add global shortcuts provider settings</li>
          <li>Speed up load of backgrounds in the Appearance settings</li>
          <li>Allow fully qualified hostnames in "Device Name" settings</li>
          <li>Fix wrong GPU names in "About" settings when using dGPU</li>
          <li>Handle GNOME Web webapps in the Application settings</li>
          <li>Make metered connection and hotspot settings adaptive to small screens</li>
          <li>Fix functionality of Wi-Fi Hotspot with multiple Wi-Fi adaptors</li>
          <li>Fix crash when removing Wi-Fi adapter</li>
          <li>Support HiDPI for tablet/stylus images in the Wacom Tablet settings</li>
          <li>Rename "left handed orientation" to "location of buttons" in the Wacom Tablet settings</li>
          <li>Fix saving of new shared folders in "Media Sharing" settings</li>
          <li>Add power consumption notice when disabling auto suspend (EU regulation)</li>
          <li>Various additional fixes, translation updates and UI/UX tweaks</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
  </releases>

